      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a driver seeking a blend of performance and reliability. The exterior is finished in a timeless coat that still holds a deep luster, though close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014honest wear for a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has been kept strictly smoke-free. The leather upholstery is supple and free of any rips or significant bolster wear, and every electronic feature, from the heated seats to the premium sound system, functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no odd noises or leaks; it has been maintained with full synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. Recent maintenance includes a fresh set of all-season tires with plenty of tread remaining and a complete brake service. It drives straight, shifts crisply, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a dependable, high-quality vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
